tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica with a T17 at the Q-School held in Buenos Aires, Argentina in January… Finished T9 at the season opening Avianca Colombia Open for his only top-10 in 9 starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica… Missed on his attempt to join PGA TOUR Canada with a T56 finish at Q-School in California in April.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played college golf at Sacramento State… Won the 2009 Wine Country Cup Amateur Championship… Reached the semifinals in the 2010 California State Amateur… Finished third at the 2009 Memorial Amateur Championship… While at Sheldon High School, he was name Delta League MVP.
tourBios.personal: Engaged to Anna Cruz, wedding date to be determined… Attended Sacramento State… Attended Sheldon High School in Elk Grove, California… Phil Dawson is his golf instructor… Favorite course he's played is Lake Merced CC… His only superstition is marking his golf ball with a purple sharpie… Favorite pro team is the San Francisco Giants… New York is his favorite city to visit… Jack Nicklaus, Bobby Jones and Ben Hogan would round out his dream foursome.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Latinoameri was T9th in 2015 at the 68 Avianca Colombia Open presentado por Arturo Calle.
